Package org.dapper.util

A package for Dapper utilities.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MatchingAlgorithm
    Defines an algorithm for matching Requirements with satisfiers.
    RequestFuture<T>
    Defines a Future specially geared toward request-response patterns.
    Requirement<S>
    Defines a matching requirement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MaximumFlowMatching
    An implementation of MatchingAlgorithm that uses the Edmonds-Karp maximum flow algorithm underneath, as provided by the JUNG project's EdmondsKarpMaxFlow class.
